childAltar.hintText: $oYe who may become a Hero...&The path to the future is open...

adultAltar.hintText: An awakening voice from the Sacred&Realm will call those destined to be&Sages, who dwell in the five temples.^$lThe awakened ones will await&for the Hero to collect&3 Medallions.^$bAnd the %revil one%w's key will&be hidden somewhere&%rin Hyrule%w.^$kTogether with the Hero of Time,&the awakened ones will return&the light of peace to the world...

ganonText: I knew I shouldn't have put the&key on the other side of my door.
ganonHintText: Ha ha ha... You'll never beat me&by reflecting my lightning bolts&and unleashing the arrows from&Gerudo Valley!
